quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  36,51,"Oo buunka baa la aafuufi10, mise kolkaa bay qubuurahooda ka soo yaaci iygoo u degdegaya xagga Rabbigood"
  36,52,"Waxay odhan doonaan: Hoog baa noo sugnaadaye! Yaa naga soo kiciyey meeshayadii aan hurudnay? Kanu waa waxa uu Raxmaanku ballan qaaday, oo Rusushii la soo diray run bay sheegeen"
  36,53,"Ma ahaaneysa wax kale aan aheyn hal Qaylo keliya, Mise kolkaa! Waxay dhammaan ahaan doonaan kuwo Hortayada la keeno"
  36,54,"Marka Maanta nafna laguma gardarroon doono in yarba ahaatee, oo ma la idinku abaal marin doono wax kale aan ahayn waxaa aad fasheen"
  36,55,"Hubaal, ehlu-Jannuhu, waxay maalin- taas ku sugnaan shuqul (la raaxeysi afooyinkooda) iyagoo aad u faraxsan"
  36,56,"Iyaga iyo afooyinkoodu waxay ku sugnaan hoosas harac ah, iyagoo ku jiqlaysan sariiro heer sare ah"
  36,57,Waxay ku lahaan midho gudaheeda oo waxay lahaan waxa ay doonaanba
  36,58,"Nabad ahaada: waa qowl uga imaan Rabbi, Naxariis Badan (Allaah Kor ahaaye)"
  36,59,Oo dhinac u bax maanta; Dambiilayaashow
  36,60,"Mawaanan idiin xil saarin Ilma Aadanow inaydaan caabudin Shaydaan? Hubaal, wuxuu idiin yahay cadow cad"
  36,61,Iyo inaad i caabudaan Aniga (Alle Keliya) Kani weeye Jidka Toosane
  36,62,Oo dhab ahaan wuxuu (Shaydaan) habaabiyey dad badan oo idinka mid ah. Mawaydaan aheyn kuwo wax garta
  36,63,Tani waa Naartii la idiinku gooddinayey
  36,64,Ee gala oo ku gubta oo gamaara iyada maanta gaalnimadiinnii darteed
  36,65,"Maalintaasi Waxaynu dabooli afafkoo- da, oo gacmahooda baa nala hadli doona, oo lugahooda baa ku marag furi doona waxay kasbadeen"
  36,66,"Oo haddii aan doonno, waxaan hubaal malaasaynaa indhahooda, markaasay hadba dhinac u cararayaan iyagoo raadinaya Jidka, Sidee bayse u arkayaan"
  36,67,"Oo haddii aan doonno, waxaan hubaal ku masakhaynaa halkooda, markaas ma karayaan inay horey u sii socdaan, mana soo noqon doonaan"